HEADWORD: Macao
<hw>Ma*ca"o</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A territory in
South China, on the Zhu Jiang river on the South China sea, formerly a
territory of Portugal. Also, the capital city of this
territory.</def>⟦br⟧
